version_description: Track 1 off the the album Worship and Believe. Not a single yet but is an excellent album opener. Marches along pretty quick. Steven Curtis Chapman tunes down a half step and capos 4, but this is written for standard tuning. Capo whatever fits vocal range. https://youtu.be/SQ3NFn9IXps.
You can simplify the song by playing just D and G in the intro and in the other parts that correspond, but this sounds closer to original. Enjoy and God bless.

song_name: As Soon As The Tide Comes In
